S|# Marketing Dashboard Research — DTC/E-Commerce (2025-2026)|> Compiled: 2026-04-05 \| For: YVON BI Dashboard (2 ventures: fashion + fintech) // ---
S|1. Top Marketing Dashboard KPIs & Metrics|### Tier 1 — The "North Star" Metrics (always visible) // \| Metric \| Definition \| DTC Benchmark \| // \|--------\|-----------\|----------------\| // \| **Blended ROAS** \| Total revenue / total ad spend (all channels) \| 3.0-5.0x for fashion, 2.5-4.0x for fintech \| // \| **NC-ROAS (New Customer ROAS)** \| Revenue from new customers / ad spend \| 2.0-3.5x (more important than blended) \| // \| **MER (mkt Efficiency Ratio)** \| Total revenue / total mkt spend \| 4.0-8.0x healthy range \| // \|
